  "name": "CHELSA-TraCE21k-centennial-bioclim (V1.0)",
  "description": "CHELSA-TraCE21k-centennial-bioclim is a global, kilometer-scale dataset generated with the CHELSA-TraCE21k downscaling model. It consists of bioclimatic and topographic variables summarized over centennial time steps from 21k BP to 0 BP.",
  "url": "https://www.chelsa-climate.org/datasets/chelsa-trace21k-centennial-bioclim",
